HEADWORD: B-52
<hw>B-52</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A large long-range bomber airplane of
the U. S. military aircraft fleet; <it>B-</it> stands for bomber. It has
the capability of delivering nuclear weapons.</def>⟦br⟧
